<Link id="l00392" /><CodeLine lineNumber="392"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// vector, which can be True or False. A DontCare is used to mask an</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00394" /><CodeLine lineNumber="394"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// operators in languages like C/C++. When comparing the evaluation of a</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00395" /><CodeLine lineNumber="395"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// condition across executed test vectors, comparisons against a DontCare</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00397" /><CodeLine lineNumber="397" lineLink="/docs/api/structs/llvm/coverage/mcdcrecord/#abfea249cd51ba9478b1e85bbc3508418"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">enum</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/coverage/mcdcrecord/#abfea249cd51ba9478b1e85bbc3508418">CondState</a> &#123; <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/coverage/mcdcrecord/#abfea249cd51ba9478b1e85bbc3508418a174b6fce191ea66ffb1e674418d159f1">MCDC&#95;DontCare</a> = -1, <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/coverage/mcdcrecord/#abfea249cd51ba9478b1e85bbc3508418a653e0944fb44b406d675db307806460c">MCDC&#95;False</a> = 0, <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/coverage/mcdcrecord/#abfea249cd51ba9478b1e85bbc3508418a3b7b1235ae7885e1f859b0abc9c11988">MCDC&#95;True</a> = 1 &#125;;</Highlight></CodeLine>
